Changelog so far: 

-Ore mines now provide direct income
-Ore mines are now upgradeable
-Ore mine competition radius now increases with upgrades
-Ore mines show lines to competing ore mines. Green if the competitor is friendly, red if it isn't a friendly
-Wealth screen now displays income from oremines
-Some hourly bonuses have been reduced
-Some hourly bonuses have been increased
-The server will no longer announce either wealth transfers or bounty increases
-Players who receive wealth from another player now get a report telling them they received a wealth transfers
-Stealth missile detection radius is now displayed on the map as a circle around the target. (Note this isn't always accurate however, as the stealth missile will be detected by a player or their radar stations, not all their structures. So if, for example, you are shooting over a player to hit a structure 100 km behind them, you're missile will be detected 100 km sooner than the circle indicates.)
-ABM silos and ICBM silos now show up separately from SAM sites and Missile sites when using the map selection rectangle
-Added "cancel decommission" button
-Each structure now has a different bounty value and player deaths pay out 10,000 or the bounty, whichever is lower. 
-Counterforce default map theme has been improved so it isn't unusable crap. 
-You can now EMP youself and your allies. (The price of the high altitude EMP has been increased.)
-Rubble value has been changed from min 25% max 75% to min 5% max 50%. 
-Decommission value has been lowered from 80% to 70%.

